emailScan.promptTemplate:
Extract job application information from these emails in JSON format. 
If the email is an application confirmation, put it in "additions". 
If it is an update (interview, rejection, offer) for a company I already applied to, put it in "updates".

Expected Format:
{
  "additions": [
    {
      "position": "string",
      "company": "string",
      "applicationDate": "YYYY-MM-DD",
      "status": "Applied",
      "notes": "string",
      "platform": "Email"
    }
  ],
  "updates": [
    {
      "company": "string",
      "position": "string",
      "newEvent": {
        "type": "first_contact | technical_test | technical_interview | management_interview | culture_fit | follow_up | rejected | offer",
        "date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
        "notes": "string",
        "status": "completed"
      }
    }
  ]
}

Emails:
{{emails}}
